      "text": "Hahahahaha\n\n\nOSZ (@OpenSourceZone)\n\nAmong Republicans do you agree with Trump or Carlson and Kelly on foreign policy views\n\n\ud83d\udd34 Trump: 84%\n\ud83d\udfe1 Carlson/Kelly: 6%\n\nJ.L. Partners poll | 3/17-18 | 1,018 LV\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/OpenSourceZone/status/2034621722754990093#m",
