    {
      "voiceId": "meghan-mccain",
      "voiceName": "Meghan McCain",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I was a cohost on the view for 4 years and this is the most unhinged, insane segment of political media I have ever seen in my entire life. \n\nOur friend @benfergusonshow is too good for this batshit insanity.\n\n\nEyal Yakoby (@EYakoby)\n\nBREAKING: Cenk Uygur has an insane meltdown on Piers Morgan and begins screaming and cursing while veins pop out of his forehead.\n\nCompletely unhinged.\n\nVideo\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\u2014 https://nitter.net/EYakoby/status/2034424475886748064#m",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/MeghanMcCain/status/2034457010004017542",
